Assembling a data set for parallel zero and first order absorption

Source: vignettes/parallel01.Rmd
parallel01.Rmd

Load puzzle

library(puzzle)

Puzzle input

nm = list(pk = list(parent=as.data.frame(puzzle::df_pk_start)),
          dose=as.data.frame(puzzle::df_dose_start),
          cov=as.data.frame(puzzle::df_cov_start))

Puzzle code

puzzle(directory=file.path(getwd()),
       order=c(0,1),
       pk=list(data=nm$pk), 
       dose=list(data=nm$dose), 
       cov=list(data=nm$cov),
       username = "Mario Gonzalez Sales")
